        "id": 1153474
      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-04-06T21:18:41Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I didn\u0027t like this either, but it doesn\u0027t make sense to me to add it to the struct minijail since that is used by the lib, and this doesn\u0027t really have anything to do with that. How would you propose I propagate the flag back to `main`?",
      "parentUuid": "3502b29f_b2d8acc1",
      "revId": "82e175283313a43a7e501c4c9f4f3ff32a9eba0b",
      "serverId": "85c56323-6fa9-3386-8a01-6480fb634889",
